snippet.title: Haxity | Introduction to the basics
snippet.description:
Wishlist Today at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/979800/Haxity/

Since we are having our Beta weekend the 3.April-5.April we wanted to teach you all the basics of Haxity. Watch this short tutorial and be ready to jump straight in and kick some ass.

If you want a Beta Key just join our Discord: https://discord.gg/7CshZ7B

If you want to know more about Haxity and its development.

Follow on social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Haxity/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayHaxity

Join the Community:
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Haxity/
